   COKE-SCHWEPPES (Undated) _ Coca-Cola Co. disclosed Friday that
its fourth-quarter performance was proving even more dismal than
the company had indicated a few weeks ago. But in an affirmation of
its goal to gain more global power in the beverage industry, the
company also announced a $1.85 billion purchase of overseas rights
to Cadbury-Schweppes soft drinks. By Constance L. Hays.
