   EUROPE-SUMMIT (Vienna) _ Developments from European Union summit
meeting. By Craig R. Whitney. 700 words.
</P>
<P>
   FRANCE-NATIONALFRONT (Paris) _ France's National Front, for
years the most powerful far-right movement in Western Europe, is in
disarray after a split among its top leaders. By Craig R. Whitney.
700 words.
