<P>
   IMPEACH (Washington) _ President Clinton donned his peacemaker's
cloak and flew to the Middle East Saturday as his aides grappled
with the ever-more-imminent prospect that he will face trial next
year in the Senate. By R.W. Apple Jr.
</P>
