<P>
   STAT OF THE WEEK
</P>
<P>
   In 27 regular-season appearances against the Jets during his
16-year career, Miami quarterback Dan Marino has 68 touchdown
passes and will try to add to that tonight. Of the 29 other
starters this weekend, 17 have fewer than 68 career touchdown
passes.
</P>
