clients of the NYTimes News Service for Sunday, Dec. 13. If you
have any questions, please call the Republic News Desk at (602)
444-8286.
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL; 
MONTINI-COLUMN (Phoenix) Two weeks before the second and final time
he was killed, Department of Public Safety officer Doug Knutson was
ALMOST killed, attacked and beaten outside his car while his
terrified wife, Sharon, huddled inside, talking to a 911 operator.
E.J. MONTINI Story will move in the ``A'' and ``K'' categories. &QL; 
