</P>
<P>
   of records about subjects like sports and business.
</P>
<P>
   3. ONE DAY MY SOUL OPENED UP, by Iyanla Vanzant.
</P>
<P>
   (Fireside/S&AMP;S, $13.) How to raise one's morale and
</P>
<P>
   realize one's ambitions. (b)
</P>
